description:
AJKB-09 EMBROIDERED CHIFFON 3 PCS

By Pcs: 3 Pcs Peshwas: Chiffon Trouser: Silk Dupatta: Chiffon Color: Navy Blue

This navy blue ensemble, reminiscent of a night sky, exudes ethereal grace. The beautifully embroidered Peshwas is adorned with a shimmering constellation of gold cupped sequins and intricately embroidered with gold zariwork that dances through colorful threads in light pink, dark pink and sage green hues. The flowing chiffon dupatta, embroidered with perfection is like a gentle breeze, completing this symphony of elegance, transforming the wearer into a timeless vision of beauty.
DESIGN DETAILS:

Embroidered front bodice on chiffon
Embroidered inner for front bodice on chiffon
Embroidered back bodice on chiffon
1.25 meter embroidered border for bodice hem on chiffon
16 embroidered Kalis for peshwas on chiffon
5 meter embroidered border for ghera on chiffon
Pair of embroidered sleeves with border on chiffon
2.5 meter embroidered dupatta with 4-side border on chiffon
1.5 meter wide-width silk for trouser
